Type: Package
Package: pvars
Title: VAR Modeling for Heterogeneous Panels
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Lennart", "Empting", , "lennart.empting@vwl.uni-due.de", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-5068-4639"))
Maintainer: Lennart Empting <lennart.empting@vwl.uni-due.de>
Description: Implements (1) panel cointegration rank tests, (2) estimators
    for panels of VAR, and (3) panel-based identification methods for
    structural vector autoregressive (SVAR) models, allowing for
    cross-sectional dependence in the error terms and for structural
    breaks in the deterministic terms of the VAR processes.
